- DC 
    DC Value
- Pulse
    ParameteKrs:
    VInitial[V],
    Von[V],
    Tdelay[s],
    Trise[s],
    Tfall[s],
    Tperiod[s],
    Ncycles
- Sine
    DC offset[V],
    Amplitude[V],
    Frequency[Hz],
    Tdelay[s],
    Theta[1/s],
    Phi[degrees],
    Ncycles 

For all other sources, the following parameters are available:
- Parasitic Properties
    Series Resistance[Ohm]
    Parallel Capacitance[F]
    show this in the schematic (yes/no)

